Type: Package
Package: collapsibleTree
Title: Interactive Collapsible Tree Diagrams using 'D3.js'
Version: 0.1.8
Authors@R: c(
    person("Patrick", "Howard", , "patrick@zevross.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("John", "Shukle", role = "ctb"))
Maintainer: Patrick Howard <patrick@zevross.com>
Description: Interactive Reingold-Tilford tree diagrams created using
    'D3.js', where every node can be expanded and collapsed by clicking on
    it.  Tooltips and color gradients can be mapped to nodes using a
    numeric column in the source data frame.  See 'collapsibleTree'
    website for more information and examples.
License: GPL (>= 3)
URL: https://github.com/zevross/collapsibleTree,
BugReports: https://github.com/zevross/collapsibleTree/issues
Depends:
    R (>= 3.0.0)
Imports:
    data.tree,
    htmlwidgets,
    methods,
    stats,
    purrr
Suggests:
